---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Children's Dentistry in Footscray | Gentle, Caring Dental Care for Kids"
  description="At Top Dentists Footscray, we provide gentle and caring dental care tailored to children's unique needs. Our experienced dentists create a friendly environment, focusing on preventive care, proper oral hygiene habits, and ensuring healthy tooth development. From regular check-ups and cleanings to dental sealants and fluoride treatments, we strive to make every visit a positive experience for your child, setting the foundation for a lifetime of healthy smiles."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-background">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <nav class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-6">
          <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2">
            <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors">Home</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li><a href="/services" class="hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors">Services</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li class="text-neutral-800 font-medium">Children's Dentistry</li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <h1 class="text-h1 font-heading font-bold text-neutral-800">
            Children's Dentistry
          </h1>
          
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              At Top Dentists Footscray, we understand that children have unique dental needs and require a gentle, caring approach. Our experienced dentists are dedicated to creating a friendly and comfortable environment for your child. We focus on preventive care, teaching proper oral hygiene habits, and ensuring your child's teeth develop properly.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              Regular check-ups and cleanings, along with dental sealants and fluoride treatments, help protect your child's teeth from decay. We strive to make every visit a positive experience, setting the foundation for a lifetime of healthy smiles.
            </p>

            <!-- Services Details -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg space-y-6 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-6">
                During your child's visit, our dentists will:
              </h3>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Gentle examination</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Gently examine their teeth and gums, checking for any signs of decay or developmental issues.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Child-friendly approach</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Use child-friendly language and techniques to explain procedures and keep your child at ease.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Digital X-rays</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Take digital X-rays, if necessary, to gain a more comprehensive view of your child's oral health.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Age-appropriate guidance</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Provide age-appropriate guidance on brushing, flossing, and healthy eating habits to maintain strong, cavity-free teeth.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Additional Information -->
            <div class="bg-primary-50 rounded-xl p-8 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-4">
                Building Positive Dental Experiences
              </h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
                We encourage regular visits to help your child build a positive relationship with dental care and prevent future problems. Our friendly approach and comfortable environment help children feel at ease during their appointments, creating positive associations with dental care that will last a lifetime.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Benefits Section -->
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800">
                  Benefits of Children's Dentistry
                </h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Early detection of dental issues</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Proper oral hygiene education</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Comfortable, child-friendly environment</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Prevention of future dental problems</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800">
                  First Visit Recommendations
                </h3>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                  <p class="text-primary-600 font-semibold text-lg mb-2">
                    Age 2-3 years or earlier
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">
                    Early visits help establish a positive relationship with dental care and catch any developmental issues early.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-primary-500 text-white text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 observe-fade">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8">
        <h2 class="text-h2 font-heading font-semibold">
          Ready to Schedule Your Child's Dental Visit?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-primary-100">
          To organise an appointment please call
          <a
            href="tel:96875050"
            class="text-white font-semibold hover:text-primary-100 transition-colors"
          >
            9687 5050
          </a>
          or press here to book online
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://apac.dentalhub.online/soe/new/%20?pid=AUTOP01"
          class="btn bg-white text-primary-500 hover:bg-primary-50 text-lg inline-block"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Book now
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>